block content
        .main-container
            .main.wrapper.clearfix
                article
                    section
                        h3 About managing your shirt:
                        br
                        h4 When you are wearing a shirtclub shirt people who see you have the ability to enter the numbers they see on your shirt and receive messages and/or personal information that you provide related to your numbers.
                        h4 Please enter as much or as little information as you like in the “Dynamic” form below.
                        h4 Please know that you can change information at any time and are able to turn viewing on and off for all entries made on your dynamic form.
                        h3 Be careful!
                        br
                        h4 The information you provided at the bar on Saturday night might not be appropriate for church on Sunday morning.
                        h4 Please mange your shirt wisely and be aware and considerate of the environment you are in.
                    section
                        h4 First Name:
                        input#first_name(value="#{user.first_name}")

                        br
                        label.radio-inline
                            input(type='radio', name='show_first_name', required='', value='1')
                            | Show Public
                        label.radio-inline
                            input(type='radio', name='show_first_name', required='', value='0')
                            | Private
                        hr

                        h4 Last Name:
                        input#last_name(value="#{user.last_name}")

                        br
                        label.radio-inline
                            input(type='radio', name='show_last_name', required='', value='1')
                            | Show Public
